title: H3L
overview: The complex Tess and her popular twin brother Thomas are new to class H3L and soon to be acquinted with the exuberant Roos, the rebellious Olivier and his best friend Faiz. Which place will they conquer in the hierarchy and how do they manage to stand their ground in H3L? Tess also keeps a video diary for her psychologist where she talks about her classmates and that is not always positive.
